title: Sign in to your VAT online account

heading_context: Sign in to your VAT online account
chunks.html_content:
Use this service to:

  • find out when your VAT returns are due
  • send an Annual Accounting Scheme VAT return if your accounting period started before 1 November 2022
  • set up a Direct Debit to pay VAT
  • view your payments and how much you owe
  • check and appeal penalties
  • report changes to your business
  • cancel your VAT registration
chunks.plain_content:
Sign in to your VAT online account
Use this service to:

  set up a Direct Debit to pay VAT

  view your payments and how much you owe

  report changes to your business
  cancel your VAT registration

heading_context: Sign in to your VAT online account
chunks.html_content: You cannot use this service to submit a quarterly VAT return.
chunks.plain_content:
Sign in to your VAT online account
You cannot use this service to submit a quarterly VAT return.

heading_context: Sign in to your VAT online account
chunks.html_content:
To use this service you need:

  • a VAT number
  • a Government Gateway user ID and password

You get these when you register for VAT.

heading_context: Sign in to your VAT online account
chunks.html_content:
You can also log in to your VAT online account to:

  • submit an EC Sales List (ESL) if you trade from Northern Ireland
  • submit a Reverse Charge Sales List (RCSL)
  • apply for EU VAT refunds if you trade from Northern Ireland
  • tell HMRC you’ve brought a vehicle into the UK using the Notification of Vehicle Arrivals (NOVA) service
  • make corrections to your VAT MOSS (Mini One Stop Shop) scheme registration information
chunks.plain_content:
Sign in to your VAT online account
Other VAT services
You can also log in to your VAT online account to:

  submit an EC Sales List (ESL) if you trade from Northern Ireland
  submit a Reverse Charge Sales List (RCSL)
  apply for EU VAT refunds if you trade from Northern Ireland
  tell HMRC you’ve brought a vehicle into the UK using the Notification of Vehicle Arrivals (NOVA) service
  make corrections to your VAT MOSS (Mini One Stop Shop) scheme registration information
